snippet.textDisplay:
Its a song which makes you actually miss someone whom you loved but couldnt be with that person...A line i can't get over is "Nadaan thi main bewafa nahi"....You just fall for someone, in an expectation to have them pick you up...while ending up dragging yourself for a few miles before getting on to your feet and moving on...Two lines i couldn't help but write:

The day i fell for you, i didn't know that it will cripple me for a while...
The day i knew u won't come, i would have died had it not been for your smile..
I think i was never cross with you....
 for leaving me with no words or maybe very few...
But The day i got up..dragging for days...all alone...
 was for the same smile and not for any effort i did or any turned stone...
